ll\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-hardware-cs#cevis (\"CEVIS Cycle Ergometer\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.exercise-prescription.resistive.modality\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for exercise-prescription.resistive.modality </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-hardware-cs#ared (\"ARED (Advanced Resistive Exercise Device)\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.exercise-prescription.resistive.exercises\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for exercise-prescription.resistive.exercises </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Squat</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Deadlift</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Heel Raise</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Bench Press</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Shoulder Press</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Bent Over Row</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Upright Row</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.weekly-adherence.missed-sessions-reason\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for weekly-adherence.missed-sessions-reason </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Operational constraints</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Equipment issues</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Crew schedule conflict</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Medical hold</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Other</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.data-delivery.archive\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for data-delivery.archive </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs#mmis (\"Medical Mission Information System\")</li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
